{"lemma":"عالَةُ","slug":"عالَةُ","root":"ع.#.ل","root_slug":"ع-_-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30147","n31067","n31261"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of عَيِّل (ʕayyil)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕi.jaːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30147","headword_ar":"عَالَّةٌ","root":"El","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and [its pls.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaAl~u","text_ar":"عَوَالُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eal~aY","text_ar":"عَلَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"epithets applied to camels [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Taking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having taken, a second draught;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so the first applied to a single she-camel]. (TA.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraDa EalaY~a sawoma EaAl~apK","text_ar":"عَرَضَ عَلَىَّ سَوْمَ عَالَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He offered to me in the manner of offering"},{"kind":"text","text":"water"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to those"},{"kind":"text","text":"(camels)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having taken, a second draught"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, O, K, TA; in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuriDa","text_ar":"عُرِضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawomu","text_ar":"سَوْمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) applied to one who offers food to him who does not need it; like the saying of the vulgar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaroDa saAbiriY~K","text_ar":"عَرْضَ سَابِرِىٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) i. e., without energy; for one does not offer drink to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EAl~p","text_ar":"عالّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"with energy, as one does to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAhilap","text_ar":"نَاهِلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or those taking, or having taken, the first draught]. (S, O, K, TA. [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 84.])"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31067","headword_ar":"عَالَةٌ","root":"Ewl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zul~ap","text_ar":"ظُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zul~ap","text_ar":"ظُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used as a shelter from the rain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constructed with cuttings of trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a manner described above:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 2, last sentence]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEaAmapN","text_ar":"نَعَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kr, K,) either as meaning The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of animal thus called"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ostrich"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zul~ap","text_ar":"ظُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", for thus"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEaAmapN","text_ar":"نَعَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies. (TA.)       -A2-  [As a pl.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiyaAlN","text_ar":"عِيَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A3-  See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eyl","text_ar":"عيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","